# ─── STEP-BY-STEP: How to set up your OpenAI API Key ───────────────────────
#
# LOCAL (VS Code / your computer):
#   1. Copy this file:  cp .env.example .env
#   2. Paste your real key below (replace sk-xxxx...)
#   3. The code will auto-load it — no restart needed.
#
# RENDER (Cloud Deployment):
#   1. Go to your Render service dashboard
#   2. Click "Environment" in the left sidebar
#   3. Click "Add Environment Variable"
#   4. Key:   OPENAI_API_KEY
#   5. Value: sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#   6. Click Save → Render auto-restarts your service
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
